title: No Published EoS by Architecture
description: All products shipped after 1997 that have no published End of Sale date that meet one of the following criteria. If covered, include all. If not covered, include: from all ship years if discovered within 3 years, shipped FY07-12 if discovered over 3 years ago, or shipped FY11+ if never discovered. Based on Net price of equipment when sold. Broken down By Architecture (Business Entity).

title: No Published EoS by Period
description: Total Migration opportunities displayed by quarter. Each quarter represent the net total value of the products that are sold within that quarter. The bar chart represents Q1.

title: No Published EoS by
description:
Sales Level - Migration's Total Actionable Opportunity for each sales level according to the sales hierarchy.

Partner - Migration's Total Actionable Opportunity for the top 100 Partners.

Customer - Migration's Total Actionable Opportunity for the top Sales Account View (SAV) names.
